  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK373">
<l>nuṇṇiya nūlpala kaṟpiṉu maṟṟuntaṉ</l>
<l>ṉuṇmai yaṟivē mikum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Athough (a man) may study the most polished treatises, the knowledge which fate has decreed to him will still prevail.</l>
            </lg>
